FBIS4-20254 "drweu083_j_94002" FBIS-WEU-94-083 Daily Report 29 Apr 1994 ITALY & VATICAN CITY Ciampi To Withdraw From Politics Ciampi To Withdraw From Politics LD2904132294 Rome RAI Due Television Network in Italian 1100 GMT 29 Apr 94 LD2904132294 Rome RAI Due Television Network Italian BFN [Text] I am not standing as a candidate in the European elections; I will not be the new leader of the opposition; I will not take part in politics. This was said by outgoing Prime Minister Carlo Azeglio Ciampi today. He was describing the work carried out by his government.
